      "message": "Line 208: `connectionFailures_` entries are never removed after their retry window expires unless a connection later succeeds or connectivity changes. Conversations can contain many historical devices, so this map can grow permanently and retain stale nodes. Remove expired entries when they become eligible, or erase entries after a retry is selected so only active backoff state is retained.\n```suggestion\nif (it !\u003d connectionFailures_.end() \u0026\u0026 it-\u003esecond.nextRetry \u003c\u003d std::chrono::steady_clock::now()) {\n    connectionFailures_.erase(it);\n    return true;\n}\n```",
